Tags:
  - Combat-Action=Orthodoxy-Ritual-Method=The Spiritual Master
  - 170
By: Swami Ramdas
---
To live and act in such a manner that the Guru is highly pleased with
the disciple is a sure condition for the working of grace. ... A true
aspirant seeks always to please his Guru by moulding his life in
accordance with his teachings.
